# Token-Free Robust NLP for Hinglish (Code-Mixed Hindi-English)

## 🚀 Overview
This research project studies **token-based** vs **token-free** models on Hinglish text:
- **mBERT** (Subword)
- **CANINE-S** (Character)
- **ByT5-small** (Byte-Level)

Goal: Evaluate **robustness to real-world noise** (typos, emojis, casing, transliteration).

