## 📊 Results Summary
Final Noise Robustness Index (NRI):

| Model | Clean Acc | Noisy Acc | NRI (%) |
|------|-----------|------------|----------|
| mBERT | 95.7% | 1.49% | **1.56%** |
| CANINE | 93.7% | 52.9% | **56.4%** |
| ByT5 | 29.7% | 27.3% | **91.9%** |

